{
  "stem": "9723.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we knew about Stalingrad, for example, when it happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Didn't know exactly what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we knew that the Germans were not very successful there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was a time when really one could hope that uh, sooner or later, uh, they would lose.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I imagine that that was one reason why they just persisted for such a long time, they-- keeping-- keeping us there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they expected that the war would be over and the Germans would be gone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her first name I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just-- I try to remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uh, uh, I don't remember her first name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, they-- they-- they stayed and talked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uh, I don't remember any specific conversations.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they would tell us about the rumors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They would tell us if there was uh, an-- any Jews were caught.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Periodically that happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Word got around that they knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, nobody we knew specifically.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mother tried to find out what happened to our father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I guess that they tried to investigate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Uh, nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Uh, then there were rumors about how the war was going, what was happening on the Western Front, what was happening on the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we talk about these things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not very long, but--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember being very cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I guess straw is a pretty good insulation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had this very thick feather quilt on top.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Winters are very cold, but we never really felt cold in the winter or hot in the summer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So other than just having to sit and lie all day, uh, it was not terribly uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah but as I said before, it's hard to imagine that we stayed there for a year and a half.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just uh, can't keep track of it day by day.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
